.DT
query_long_details
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_long_details

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_long_details -  This method returns extra details about the object that should be known above the basic long.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string query_long_details(string arg,
int dark,
object looker)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^arg%^RESET%^ - the argument the look was called with
%^BOLD%^dark%^RESET%^ - how dark the place is
%^BOLD%^looker%^RESET%^ - the person looking at the object

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/basic/desc.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns extra details about the object that should be
known above the basic long.  This is printed to people who do not
own the object in question (long() is used if you own it).
.EP

